doc.previous: New York s initial electoral vote certificate indicated that all of its 31 electoral votes for president were cast for John L Kerry of Massachusetts instead of John F Kerry who won the popular vote in the state 41 This was apparently the result of a typographical error and an amended electoral vote certificate with the correct middle initial was transmitted to the President of the Senate prior to the official electoral vote count 42
